admin.title: Raazi
admin.overview: An Indian spy is married to a Pakistani military officer during the Indo-Pakistani War of 1971.

admin.title: Khushi
admin.overview: While playing matchmaker to a pair of their friends, two young university students begin developing feelings for each other.

admin.title: Dhadkan
admin.overview: Dhadkan is about Anjali (Shilpa Shetty) who is a girl that hails from an extremely rich and influential family. Her father Mr. Chauhan (Kiran Kumar) is a renowned businessman and has many dreams for his daughter. But Anjali is in love with Dev (Sunil Shetty) who is very poor & often cannot even afford to clothe himself properly. Dev also loves Anjali, wants to marry her so has to meet her father.

admin.title: Dhadkanein
admin.overview: Romance - Star-crossed lovers Raj (Attin Bhalla) and Sandhya (Preeti Mehra) must challenge disapproving families, corrupt police, ruthless gangsters and outdated traditions if their love is to have a chance. Sandhya's pimp father has always wanted her for his flesh trade and arranges to sell her to a Bombay kingpin. With an underworld army on their heels, the lovers become fugitives; running for their lives ... and for love. -  Attin Bhalla, Preeti, Kader Khan

user1.title: Training Day
user1.overview: On his first day on the job as a narcotics officer, a rookie cop works with a rogue detective who isn't what he appears.
